en:
When the world?s news leaves us speechless, art is the antidote. Summer is also a time to pause
to take a break, to step back and look to the future with greater serenity.

La ferme de Cantagrel, with its wide range of activities, opens its doors to the public all summer long, offering a chance to combine summertime carefreeness with the power of art.

Come and discover the fifth season of Sous les Étoiles, which we have imagined as a letter to multiple recipients, an invitation to :
- To oneself, the opportunity to go out, to free oneself, to express oneself, to get ready;
- To everyone, the opportunity to come together, share, embrace, dance and laugh;
- With friends, the joy of applauding, celebrating and celebrating;
- As a family, the pleasure of feasting, remembering, growing;
- Together, the energy to build, dream, poetize, continue?

Sous les Étoiles is an independent event that exists thanks to its audience. Thank you all for bringing this adventure to life and for being our best ambassadors.

